title: This Week - S13E18 - 2015.02.05 - 468p x264
description:
POLITICAL: This Week
On: BBC 1 HD    
Date: Thursday 5th February 2015 
Time: 23:45 to 00:30 

Andrew Neil presents a round-up of the week with Alan Johnson, Michael Portillo and Miranda Green. They are joined by comedian and Labour supporter Matt Forde, who looks at Ed Miliband and the party's links to business. There is a film rounding up the week from Anne McElvoy, and former Blue Peter presenter Helen Skelton joins the panel to look at 'stuffiness' in the week a TV documentary showed Parliament from behind the scenes. Crack open the Blue Nun and prepare to watch public service broadcasting at its best.
